'''R-65 heavy blaster''' was used by the [[Royal Naboo Security Forces|Naboo Security Guards]]. The blaster shot twin energy bolts that could bounce off walls and other solid objects. The energy bolts could pierce through armor, whereas regular blaster shots couldn't.

The R-65 was [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Quarsh Panaka/Legends|Quarsh Panaka's]] personal blaster. His R-65 was a twin-bolt model of the standard guard [[CR-2 heavy blaster pistol/Legends|CR-2 heavy blaster pistol]].

